messages.text: I don't have one. I just don't what you want me to say cody?

Well fuck. Every time I get a fgirlfriend we agree. No strings attached. I understand you miss me and I understand you love me. And IU'm, sorry we broke up. But you have to understand I don't give second chances. You said you be able to be mature about this so do it. You might not wanna hear this or you will deny it but try being honest for once.
